    Hearing Voluois message he instantly got up and flew away. Going as fast 
as he could he landed after a while. He say Battera talking to someone new, 
he wondered if this might be the famed Voluois.
    He walked up and punched at the guy aiming for the jaw. It was for all 
the crying that he had caused Battera.
    "Sorry for that, I needed to get it out of my system," He said right 
after.
